Dialogue: 12,0:21:09.31,0:21:10.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Em xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 12,0:21:10.93,0:21:12.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Giờ sao đây?
Dialogue: 12,0:21:18.00,0:21:19.93,Main,,0,0,0,,"Popcorn Wizard"
Dialogue: 12,0:21:20.27,0:21:21.38,Main,,1200,0,0,,Chính chủ à?
Dialogue: 12,0:21:21.38,0:21:22.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Không thể nào.
Dialogue: 12,0:21:23.80,0:21:26.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chơi!
Dialogue: 12,0:21:26.58,0:21:29.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Khá lắm! Quả "Chán Chường Vô Vị" ấy.
Dialogue: 12,0:21:29.77,0:21:33.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Đằng ấy là người đầu tiên \Ndồn được tôi đến mức này đấy!
Dialogue: 12,0:21:34.77,0:21:36.06,Main,,0,0,0,,À... à...
