Dialogue: 12,0:21:39.05,0:21:40.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hẹn gặp lại! Bai!
Dialogue: 12,0:21:40.93,0:21:42.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Đợi đã, Popcorn!
Dialogue: 12,0:21:44.57,0:21:45.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Cúp máy rồi.
Dialogue: 12,0:22:06.46,0:22:10.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Chơi!
